OL,4,G0100FFace the Music
OL,5,     GJoseph Cooper invites viewers to
OL,6,     Gmatch their musical wits against
OL,7,     Gguests Joyce Grenfell, Robin Ray
OL,8,     Gand Richard Baker. With guest
OL,9,     Gmusician Alfredo Campoli.
OL,10,G0130FSeven Worlds, One Planet
OL,11,     GAntarctica - the coldest,
OL,12,     Gwindiest, most hostile continent.
OL,13,     GOnly the toughest can survive
OL,14,     Ghere. But the ocean here is
OL,15,     Gwarming and with that comes an
OL,16,     Guncertain future.
OL,17,G0230FRaiders of the Lost Past with
OL,18,     FJanina Ramirez
OL,19,     GA lost thousand-year-old ship
OL,20,     Gtransforms the fierce reputation
OL,21,     Gof the Vikings.
